---
title: "SSD UC7 — Idea Workshop"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as ":User"
    participant S as ":System"

    Note over User,S: System treated as BLACK BOX<br/>UC7 — Idea Workshop (Multi-turn Ideation)

    User->>S: startWorkshopSession(mode)
    S-->>User: sessionStarted(sessionId, greeting)

    loop until all requirements collected
        User->>S: sendWorkshopMessage(sessionId, message)
        S-->>User: agentResponse(message, requirementsCollected, requirementsNeeded, isReady)
    end

    S-->>User: requirementsComplete(summary, confirmationMessage)

    User->>S: confirmAndGenerate(sessionId, confirmed: true)

    loop system generating story
        S-->>User: progressUpdate(stage, message)
    end

    S-->>User: storyGenerated(storyId, title, scenes[], pdfPath)
